title: Hyper-V Cluster Nodes
agents: windows
catalog: os/windows
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the defined nodes on a Hyper-V cluster.

 In order to run, its needed to copy the hyperv_cluster.ps1 script to the plugin
 folder of the agent.

item:
 Name of the node.

inventory:
 All cluster nodes found will be inventorized.

